## Tables Tab — Table Access

The first tab (**Tables**) shows all tables in the vault. Use this to control which tables the AI can query during the conversation.

### Enabling a Table

1. Open the Chat Context panel and click the **Tables** tab.
2. Find the table you want to enable.
3. Click the toggle to turn it **On**.
4. Set the access level:
   - **Read** — The AI can read and query data from this table
   - **R/W** — The AI can read and also write or update records in this table

### Disabling a Table

Click the toggle on any enabled table to turn it **Off**. The AI will no longer include that table's data in its responses.

<Tip>
Enable only the tables relevant to your question for more focused and accurate responses.
</Tip>

