## Connections Tab — Connection Actions

The third tab (**Connections**) shows actions available from your vault's connected external systems, grouped by connection. Enabling a connection action allows the AI to interact with that external system as part of its response.

**Examples by connection type:**

| Connection | Available Actions |
|------------|------------------|
| **EHR (Epic)** | Send HL7 Message to EHR, Received HL7 Message from EHR |
| **SFTP File Server** | Upload File, Download File, Delete File, Move File, New File Uploaded, File Modified, File Deleted |
| **OR Vitals Monitor** | Data Received from Device |
| **Graphium EMR** | Create Case, Update Case, Case Created, Case Updated, Case Signed |
| **Google Sheets** | Add Row, Update Row, Delete Row, Create Sheet, Row Added, Row Updated, Sheet Modified |
| **Graphium Surveys** | Create Survey, Survey Completed |

The exact connections and actions you see depend on what your vault has configured. Toggle individual actions on or off within each connection group.

